%N A392006 Indices corresponding to records in A392071.
%e A392006 880 is in this sequence because d(880) = 20 and d(882) = 18, so the minimum value is 18. And there is no number k < 880 where min(d(k), d(k+2)) >= 18.
%e A392006 The sequence min(d(n),d(n+2)) starts with 1, 2, 2, 3, 2, 4, 2, 4, 2, 4, 2, 4, 2, 4, 2, 5, 2, 6, 2, 4,... at n=1 and sets records of 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 8, ... at its positions 1, 2, 4, 6, 16,...
%o A392006 (PARI)
%o A392006 print1(r=1); for(n=2, 1e5, if(min(numdiv(n), numdiv(n+2))>r, r=min(numdiv(n), numdiv(n+2)); print1(", "n)))
